Usage: list_libraries [-help] [-power_domain <string>] [-used] [-used_analysis]
                      [-view <string>]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-power_domain <string>     # The power domain from which instances are to be
                           # selected. (string, optional)
-used                      # To print list of libraries used in the design and
                           # all other libraries whose voltages match the
                           # voltages of the used libraries (bool, optional)
-used_analysis             # To print list of used libraries in the design
                           # (bool, optional)
-view <string>             # The view name whose libraries will be listed
                           # (string, optional)